headline: Will FactSet’s (FDS) AI Integration With Macrobond Reinforce Its Edge in Financial Data Analytics?
summary: Earlier in October 2025, Macrobond announced a strategic integration with FactSet, enabling Macrobond users to directly access FactSet’s extensive equity and ETF datasets, such as fundamentals, consensus estimates, and market aggregates, within the Macrobond platform. This collaboration brings together Macrobond’s macroeconomic insights and FactSet’s detailed company analysis, aiming to empower clients with a seamless way to integrate global economic trends and security-level intelligence...
